{"tid":195881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"事實上大部份香港人都樂於現狀","createTime":"2017-04-11T02:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T11:23:39.000Z","uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"afdb11fc6643818fcd0c811f010e036dc19e8fe3","tid":195881,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:20:26.000Z","msg":"大部份香港人樂於現狀<br />\n大部份支持正苦口中講的安全繁榮<br />\n<br />\n根本想變的人只係少數大部分人包括：<br />\n<br />\n公務員<br />\n地產霸權<br />\n商家<br />\n狗官<br />\n新移民<br />\n綜援人仕<br />\n愛國人仕<br />\n親中人士<br />\n供樓人仕<br />\n有父幹人仕<br />\n炒樓人仕<br />\n有錢人<br />\n離地人仕<br />\n持有外國護照人仕<br />\n廢老<br />\n<br />\n他們都不想香港改變現有狀況<br />\n支持香港繼續繁榮穩定，不要破壞香港和諧"},{"pid":"2f3e75d8d25fb741019e7b740e1e6ca633da8aca","tid":195881,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:22:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">事實上大部分香港人都唔配做人！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"eb6f230fa57256d2cacc93e6ddf696155fefc80c","tid":195881,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:29:23.000Z","msg":"佢地先係真正既香港人"},{"pid":"29c38d73d1e155175bbb36b2296a4fe8ca7742e6","tid":195881,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:38:51.000Z","msg":"扣晒個個LIST 就係淨返窮撚,青年人,學生"},{"pid":"c41d70f2e344939cff94307bcb67074947b17627","tid":195881,"uid":71462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:49:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扣晒個個LIST 就係淨返窮撚,青年人,學生</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d52ab1c1fdd5aec664f0409ff27dbbdaa59a6a","tid":195881,"uid":71462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扣晒個個LIST 就係淨返窮撚,青年人,學生</blockquote><br />\n三重身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4190079640835ed547cf41a011583c5147